=== Linux Documentation Project ===
These are packages from Linux Documentation Project, to create a wiki page in your language with all <nowiki>[[http://translationproject.org/PO-files/|LDP]]</nowiki> modules and their Launchpad respective links, you need to save the lines below as text file and replace the language extension.

=== Using in you language ===
Suggestion: sed -i 's/es\/pt_BR/es\/de/g' text_file

Example: sed -i 's/es\/pt_BR/es\/es/g' text_file (to spanish language)
